summary:
David Tennant And The Cast Of Camping In Juliette Lewis' New Music Video   

David Tennant and his fellow Camping cast members...
caption:
David Tennant And The Cast Of Camping In Juliette Lewis’ New Music Video 

David Tennant and his fellow Camping cast members have appeared in a hilarious new music video for their camp mate Juliette Lewis’ cover of the 80s track, Tell It To My Heart.
The track was produced by Ben Lee and Brad Wood and the video which was directed by Ione Skye also features Jennifer Garner, Bridget Everett, Brett Gelman, Chris Sullivan, Cheyenne Haynes and Arturo Del Puerto.
